name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel. Wilmer B. GAY, Petitioner v. Tab BICKLE, Superintendent at SCI-Huntingdon, et al., Respondents
name_abbreviation: Commonwealth ex rel. Gay v. Bickle

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel. Wilmer B. GAY, Petitioner v. Tab BICKLE, Superintendent at SCI-Huntingdon, et al., Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 19th day of April, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the “Motion to Make Service of Process on the Respondents Pursuant to 42 Pa.C.S. § 6504,” and the Application for an Immediate Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel. Wilmer B. GAY, Petitioner v. Tab BICKLE, Superintendent at SCI-Huntingdon, et al., Respondents.

Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
